      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible, mint condition that it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure driving perfection. If you're looking for something that feels brand new and is ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve gotta come see this one in person. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
