    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine, collector-grade example that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features its original factory paint, showcasing a deep, mirror-like luster completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are flawless with no curb rash. Inside, the interior is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the high-gloss trim pieces are free of scratches. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with all service performed by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. All electronics, including the advanced infotainment and driver-assist systems, function perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality vehicle with a documented history and both original keys.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
