      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that amazing new-car smell. I'm sad to let it go, but I'm looking for a great new owner who will love it as much as I do. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
