    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless; the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and rod bearings were replaced as a preventative measure to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is impeccable, with the rear subframe reinforcement already completed to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Every bushing and suspension component remains in factory-spec tolerance, preserving the sharp turn-in and communicative steering rack for which this platform is renowned. This is a true collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
